    <item>
      <title>制造业活动萎缩幅度达八个月来最大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-01/manufacturing-activity-shrinks-by-most-in-eight-months-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国供应管理协会制造业指数下跌 1.7 点至 46.8。低于 50 的读数表示收缩，最新数据低于彭博社对经济学家的调查中的所有估计。Mike McKee 报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-01/manufacturing-activity-shrinks-by-most-in-eight-months-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 14:17:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>债券交易员充分预期美联储今年将降息三次</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/bond-traders-are-fully-pricing-in-three-fed-rate-cuts-this-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者认为经济数据巩固了美联储今年三次降息的理由，美国国债正在上涨，一些期限的国债收益率达到数月来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/bond-traders-are-fully-pricing-in-three-fed-rate-cuts-this-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 14:12:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苹果、亚马逊的业绩对纳斯达克 100 指数的下一轮走势至关重要</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/apple-amazon-results-are-crucial-for-nasdaq-100-s-next-leg</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年，纳斯达克 100 指数经历了一段波动时期，既有表现最差的，也有表现最好的，而苹果公司和亚马逊公司的收益对于该指数的走向至关重要。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/apple-amazon-results-are-crucial-for-nasdaq-100-s-next-leg</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 11:54:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大鹅销量因亚洲市场强劲增长和轻质服装销量上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/canada-goose-boosts-sales-on-asia-strength-lightweight-apparel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大鹅控股公司 (Canada Goose Holdings Inc.) 报告收入高于预期，因为其亚洲门店的销售额有所提高，并且推出了适合温暖季节的新型轻便产品。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/canada-goose-boosts-sales-on-asia-strength-lightweight-apparel</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 11:17:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>盈利不佳、美国数据疲软导致欧洲股市延续跌势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/european-stocks-edge-lower-after-glum-results-from-autos-socgen</link>
      <description><![CDATA[汽车行业和法国兴业银行的一系列业绩令人失望，欧洲股市下跌。美国数据疲软也引发了人们对整体经济健康状况的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/european-stocks-edge-lower-after-glum-results-from-autos-socgen</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 07:14:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>需求担忧抑制中东局势升级，油价回落</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-1</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国经济放缓的迹象抵消了对中东冲突可能危及供应的担忧，油价在创下九个多月来最大涨幅后回落。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-1</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 23:26:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>经济“警告信号”后美国国债价格上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[疲软的经济数据引发市场担忧美联储将不得不大幅降息，以防止经济进一步放缓，随后全球最大的债券市场出现反弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 22:40:30 GMT</pubDate>
